column5: APDN Dr Thandeka R Kunene is the Founder and Visionary of House of Hemp HoH in Johannesburg South Africa Dr Kunene serves as Chief Executive Officer of House of Hemp Pty Ltd She worked for several years for UNIDO and the Commonwealth Secretariat before launching her own business Dr Kunene is a leader in the developing cannabis and hemp industries in South Africa her knowledge experience and highlevel government connections span across decades of research and development of cannabis and hemp in SA For 15 years she has been a key promoter of natural fibres in South Africa and hemp in particular to alleviate poverty and fight environmental degradation She serves as Director of House of Hemp Pty Ltd Dr Kunene serves as Member of Advisory Board at Global Hemp Group Inc She was instrumental in creating the National Hemp Foundation and Global Natural Fibre Forum
